data.description: This newer home is nestled in an established area of Jubilee! With it comes access to the many beautiful ammenities this community has to offer, including a pool, tennis courts, and security of a gated community. This home features walkin shower in the master bathroom, open floor plan, and easy access. The kitchen features beautiful appliances, and nice breakfast nook. Yard is small with easy to care for landscaping. Come take a look at the well cared for home!
